 
<p>
US government "security" agencies <a href="https://www.politico.com/news/2022/07/18/dhs-location-data-aclu-00046208">track people's movements</a> through their
phones, without getting search warrants, by buying location data from
companies that accumulate them.
<p>
We must forbid companies from collecting, or accumulating, people's
location data.

 